### Create Coupon (admin only)
# @name createCoupon
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/coupons
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "code": "SAVE10",
  "discountType": "percentage",
  "discountValue": 10,
  "minOrderValue": 500,
  "expiresAt": "2026-12-31T00:00:00.000Z",
  "usageLimit": 5
}

### Get All Coupons (admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/coupons
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Create Order — With Valid Coupon Applied
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "items": [
    { "product": "{{productId}}", "quantity": 1 }
  ],
  "address": "{{addressId}}",
  "idempotencyKey": "test-coupon-{{$timestamp}}",
  "couponCode": "SAVE10"
}

### Create Order — Invalid Coupon Code (should 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "items": [
    { "product": "{{productId}}", "quantity": 1 }
  ],
  "address": "{{addressId}}",
  "idempotencyKey": "test-badcoupon-{{$timestamp}}",
  "couponCode": "FAKECODE"
}

### Create Order — Order Below minOrderValue (should 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "items": [
    { "product": "{{productId}}", "quantity": 1 }
  ],
  "address": "{{addressId}}",
  "idempotencyKey": "test-lowvalue-{{$timestamp}}",
  "couponCode": "SAVE10"
}